A friend of mine lives in SoHo, and she told me SVU was filming right on her street, so of course, after work, Shauna (
lilprincess26
) and i went. We thought oh hey we'll go watch them film for a bit. Well they were filming indoors so there wasnt much to see. BUT.. at dinner call, who came out right in front of us? Thats right! Adam Beach!! He was so much more handsome in person. He was being silly.. they had some pizza rolls and he says, very loudly I might add.. I LOVE TOSTINO PIZZA ROLLS!!... it was too cute. So after he was finished eating, I asked one of the handlers there if I could possibly get a pic with Adam since there was NOONE around watching the filming. She went over and asked him, he smiled and came over. I wanted to melt right then and there. He was like, Hi I'm Adam Beach! and shook my hand.. ohh it was so cool.. he was like want to take a picture?? duh!! so he posed with Shauna, then one with myself and one with our friend Jill.. he was so very nice! and short! hahahaa.. anyways he went back across the street, and a while later, this guy was standing by us. Lo and behold it was Mariska's bodyguard. He asked us if we wanted to meet Mariska too and I was like :O duh!! We had told him that we run Diane's website and he was like, I LOVE Diane, she's amazing! You tell her Tom the Security Guard says hi! i'm like :O and when Mariska came out he's like, call her over girls! I'm like, MARISKA! ....andddd she came over and we got pictures with her too! She was very very sweet in person. she's extremely friendly, she was laughing and she loved that i had a Fearlessness necklace on..  She is even MORE gorgeous in person...she stayed and chatted with us for a few mins and then she had to go see August =)  I thought it was nice of her to take time to take a picture with us, even tho she was on her way to see the baby. Anyways.. I am STILL stoked.. I cant believe I met both of them!

Check 'em out behind the cut!


The signage! 




Here is where they were filming.. INSIDE the building lol


there's Adam Beach!  in the jacket!

Adam eating dinner.. *giggle*


and then he came over to take the pic!!!

with Adam!!




Adam Beach and I!  I was so sick, thats why I look blah =(



it started to get dark out, and they wouldnt let us use flash.. but there's adam again lol

and here comes Mariska!!!


Gah!  Gorgeous woman!


Mariska again

and.. the best photo ever..  Jill, Shaun, Mariska & me!

A challenge of watching 100 movies in 2007. 

Rules:

- Can include Cinema, DVD or on TV
- Can enter (write down) a film that I have seen previous to 2007 but watch again this year
- Cannot enter (write down) a film twice

Star Ratings:

~ - Very bad movie, doesn't even deserve one star
* - Didn't like it, wouldn't wanna watch it again.
** - Good movie, wouldn't buy it on DVD though.
*** - Good movie, might buy it or already did.
**** - Great movie. I'll probably buy it or at least watch it again.
***** - Awesome. One of my favorite movies.

So Law and Order: Criminal Intent was filming outside of my work and INSIDE my work...the extras holding room was on the 6th floor right across the hall from us! They were gonna be filming in the lobby of our building later on at night, around 9pm lol so we didnt see that cause we didnt feel like waiting around, lol. We got to see some during the day and then some more when we were leaving work at night (that would be why some of the pics are REALLY dark, they wouldnt allow us to use a flash). The episode is going to be about a Rapper getting shot, you will see the "memorial" that they have set up. Also some of the pics are blurry lol cause they were going through rehearsal and constanting moving, plus ALL the people around kept getting in the way LOL. So I hope you like the pics that we were able to snag :) We were also able to snag a short vid of them rehearsing with Shaunas digital camera:)











































and the vid!

Okay so yeah today started off bad, i was feeling super super sick like the start of the flu but i went to work because we were leaving at noon to go be in the audience of Rachel Rays talk show, we got there around 12:30ish with a line already forming so we waited, we got in and the warm up guy told us how lucky we were cause there was a big celeb and it was a "giving season" lol we got in and guess what we got? 

a 100 dollar gift card from american express!!! 100 dollars!!! lol it was SOOOO awesome...we got some cookies and then she gave EVERYONE a nintendo ds handheld gaming system!!! holy shit that thing is worth like 150 bucks!!! and a free game!!!!!!! more snacks and SOO much fun!! Wynona Judd was the celeb guest, she was pretty damn funny!

Rachel is about 100 times prettier in person, much skinner in person and shorter lol, she was really funny, joked in between takes, ect =) it was a lot of fun!

we didnt finish until 7pm (2 partial shows were filmed so i will be in the audience for 2 shows!) and i have a MASSIVE migraine, not eating since 9am and basically the flu will do that to ya lol but it was SO worth it!!! 


Greys is on so lata, more to share tomorrow!
